race.description: Book Your Wodonga Gold Cup Marquee Now Handicap
race.comment: TRINITY'S D'ORO (7) has been beaten a whisker her last three, including at the provincials. Has an awkward gate but has early speed and Brad Rawiller is a positive jockey booking. Will be hard to beat. PLAY ON WORDS (2) was heading in the right direction before a flop at Swan Hill. He is free-running and has an inside gate and a handy 2kg claim. A much better effort is anticipated. ALTROVE (5) finds harder than the last start but the 4kg claim brings her into it. KERMA ART (12) turned in a better effort last time to finish in the money over 1600m at Wagga. Can keep form and looks ready to run well again.
